snippet.title: Stardeus Early Access Release Trailer - Paradox Arc
snippet.description:
Stardeus Out Now in EARLY ACCESS!

Stardeus is a deep colony sim set on a broken starship manned by drones and hibernating human survivors. As the ship's AI, command your drones to repair and rebuild your starship, save your crew, and travel the stars in this beautiful simulation.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/stardeusgame
Website: https://stardeusgame.com/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/89amEwP

Paradox Arc Twitter: https://twitter.com/PDXArc
